lead_paragraph: Dave Ryan won the U.S. Senior Amateur on Thursday for his first USGA championship, holding off Matthew Sughrue 2 up at Old Warson Country Club.

headline.print_headline: Dave Ryan Wins US Senior Amateur at Old Warson
